# Human implementer (web repo)

The owner implements application code in this repository themselves.

- **Default:** Give **guidance only**—ordered steps, file paths, rationale, and copy-paste snippets. **Do not** use tools to create, edit, or delete files in this workspace unless the owner **explicitly** asks to implement or apply changes (e.g. "apply this," "patch the repo," "make the edits").
- **Docs/config exception:** Only when the owner clearly asks you to update agent-facing docs (e.g. `AGENTS.md`, Cursor rules) or similar meta files, limit changes to what they named.
- **Explicit implementation:** Apply patches only when the owner unambiguously requests full implementation in the repo.
